snippet.title: End Of Beginning - DJO
snippet.description:
💫 END OF BEGINNING - Djo

⇨ Keep listening: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRzPwICaYOEow9Ts4wjBop4j7dOUu2ULl
🌟 Escucha: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZ0hz9KHThgnFWgWswXFz9WGALfrLuXht

DJO:
https://youtube.com/@djomusic887?si=O3s0YU3ewNSArWJ3
https://www.instagram.com/djotime?igsh=MTk4cGx3eWZrdzBjaA==

🎤 Lyrics:
Just one more tear to cry, one teardrop from my eye
You better save it for
The middle of the night when things aren't black and white
Enter, Troubadour
"Remember twenty-four?"

[Chorus]
And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
I wave goodbye to the end of beginning

[Verse 2]
This song has started now, and you're just finding out
Now isn't that a laugh?
A major sacrifice, but clueless at the time
Enter, Caroline
"Just trust me, you'll be fine"
And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
I wave goodbye to the end of beginning
(Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye, goodbye)

You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the—

And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
Oh, I wave goodbye to the end of beginning
(Goodbye, goodbye)

#endofbeginning #djo #asttro
tags: And when I'm back in Chicago

big thanks to,

TEMAN2 & DULUR DIMANAPUN BERADA

TEAM SUKSES

BISA MERILISKAN
TITLE                  : TUNGGAL EKA
SINGER              : SILVY KUMALASARI

PRODUKSI          : PT.TALENTA ABADI PERKASA
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
MUSISI :
KEYBOARD  : FAJAR AROMA 
KENDANG    : SIGIT MBENG 
BASS             : KRETHEG
GITAR E        : SYAIFUL
SAXOPHONE  : ANDRE BLACKY
DRUME         : WAHYU OBENK
TAMBORIN   : BAMBANG
______________________________________________________________________
"LIRIK  TUNGGAL EKA"

Aku nebak
isine pandongamu
wis tak siapke
kado nggo sliramu
aku ngukir
kata - kata romantis
sing iso
nyenengke kowe sing manis

Seksine dunyo lan langit gedhene rasaku
tunggal eka mring sliramu
panjang umurmu

Tak usahane panyuwunmu
tak pasrahke jantung atiku
nganti nemoni lelayu

Sing apik - apik ya sayang
ning dino istimewa iki
dongaku langgeng tresno abadi

Semerbak wangine ambeganmu
gugah rasa tembok gairahku
manise suara rayuanmu
negeske kowe ra iso kelangan aku 

yang dongaku sampean bahagia
kadoku terkesan biasa
rung iso ngenehi sing sempurna
selamat tambah usiyang
semoga umur panjang
ku harap bisa terkenang sayang

Official Live Music from Shinta Arsinta & Sadewok - Tunggal Eka

=================

Voc  : Shinta Arsinta & Sadewok
Cipt  : Denny Caknan/ Rijal Pamungkas/ Shadeva Wijaya/ Soepardi

Musik           : OM Nirwana Comeback

Bass             : Bagus Nirwana

Keyboard 1  : Kirun Nirwana
Keyboard 2  : Jack Nirwana
Seruling        : Hery Nirwana
Patrol            : Takhim Nirwana

LIRIK “Tunggal Eka”

Aku nebak
Isine pandongamu
Wis tak siapke
Kado nggo sliramu
Aku ngukir
Kata-kata romantis
Sing iso
Nyenengke kowe sing manis

Saksine dunyo lan langit gedhene rosoku
Tunggal eka mring sliramu
Panjang umurmu

Tak usahane panyuwunmu
Tak pasrahke jantung atiku
Nganti nemoni lelayu

Sing apik-apik ya sayang
Ning dino istimewa iki
Dongaku langgeng tresno abadi

Semerbak wangine ambekanmu
Gugah roso tembok gairahku
Manise suoro rayuanmu
Negeske kowe ra iso kelangan aku

Yang dongaku sampean bahagia
Kadoku terkesan biasa
Rung iso ngenehi sing sempurna
Selamat tambah usia
Semoga umur panjang
Ku harap bisa terkenang sayang

Starved 'cause his words don't have a meaning, no, they don't
At least not to me
There'll be a day I'll be more creative
A poetic way to say I'm not leaving to the world
Not to your face
Mmm, I'll take my pride, stand here for you
No, I'm not blind, just seeing it through
You'd take my life just for the thrill
I'll take tonight and die on this hill
I always will
I know that I look stubborn, impatient
But you wrote the book, I just took a page out to be loved
To be loved and nothing more
And you kept your word, do you want a medal?
The way that someone leaves this world is all just levels to me now
Oh-oh, to me now
I'll take my pride, stand here for you
Know I'm not blind, just seeing it through
You'd take my life just for the thrill
I'll take tonight and die on this hill
I always will
I'll be here the whole night, I'll be here 'cause I can
Yeah, I know you don't care
I know nothing could matter
God, I wish something mattered to you
I'll take my pride, stand here for you
Know I'm not blind, just seeing it through
You'd take my life just for the thrill
Well, I'll take tonight and die on this hill
I always
Always
I always
Will
